description: It all starts with choosing a quality training provider to help you get certified and job-ready as you enter the fitness industry.
The Certificate III in Fitness will provide you with the foundation skills and knowledge you need to turn your passion for fitness into a profession.
This higher level qualification will open up an array of career possibilities not currently available when holding the Certificate III in Fitness only.
AFA has teamed up with the experts at LEAN Nutrition Tech on their revolutionary new meal planning platform, Health & Physical By LEAN.
